prodNameC: 羅氏可霸斯免疫分析癌胚抗原檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagents - working solutions
M     Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 8 mL: 
       Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL; preservative.
R1    Anti-CEA-Ab~biotin (gray cap), 1 bottle, 10 mL:
       Biotinylated monoclonal anti-CEA antibody (mouse/human) 3.0 mg/L;
       phosphate buffer 100 mmol/L, pH 6.0; preservative.
R2    Anti-CEA-Ab~Ru(bpy)2+3 (black cap), 1 bottle, 8 mL:
       Monoclonal anti-CEA antibody (mouse) labeled with ruthenium
       complex 4.0 mg/L; phosphate buffer 100 mmol/L, pH 6.5; preservative.

CalSet - working solutions
• CEA Cal1: 2 bottles, each containing 1.0 mL of calibrator 1
• CEA Cal2: 2 bottles, each containing 1.0 mL of calibrator 2
CEA (human, from cell culture) in two concentration ranges (approx. 5 ng/mL and approx. 50 ng/mL) in a buffer/protein matrix. 1 ng/mL CEA corresponds to 16.9 mIU/mL.
applicantName: 台灣羅氏醫療診斷設備股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民權東路3段2號10樓
efficacy: 用於體外定量檢測人類血清及血漿中癌胚抗原的免疫分析法。Elecsys CEA分析法是進一步適用於CEA的連續測量, 藉以輔助癌症病患的治理。Electro-chemiluminescence immunoassay “ECLIA”是預定使用於 Elecsys和cobas e免疫分析儀上。
